br.ufrj.ct.ruadmin

Class Meal

  • java.lang.Object
    • br.ufrj.ct.ruadmin.Meal

  • public class Meal
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by Felipe Podolan Oliveira on 29/09/17. This is the Meal class, with same attributes as the backend. The attributes are named in a manner that it facilitates the conversion of a Meal object and a meal json (received from the backend) by using the Gson library. Meals can also be created from Spreadsheets using the Google docs API.
